Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.13,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are to light the lanterns hidden in the forest around us.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.68,0:00:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're within 500 meter radius around the camp.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who can bring back a lit lantern without the fire going out during the next three days
Dialogue: 2,0:00:25.65,0:00:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will receive the permission to take part in missions.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.60,0:00:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are only three lanterns.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.22,0:00:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that there are only three permissions.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a dark forest. You'll be found out right away.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.78,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you not to use your flames.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.63,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This training is designed to turn us against each other.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.88,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we do that...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be suicide.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.90,0:01:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what? There's so many of them!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they blood-suckers? Demon bugs?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.27,0:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I humbly call upon the Gods of Harvest!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow my wishes, leave none unfulfilled!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.18,0:01:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ni, give me something for bug repellent!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.27,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ni!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.41,0:01:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:32.64,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi! Shiemi!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.78,0:01:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.95,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Konekomaru.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he found a lantern.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.98,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it's impossible alone, we've gotta work together.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,20,,You were right, this is impossible alone.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.26,0:02:15.54,Default,,0,0,20,,When I saw it, I thought maybe we had misinterpreted the mission...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.54,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,20,,Yeah. This training requires cooperation.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.55,0:02:26.15,Default,,0,0,20,,Rin, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.75,Default,,0,0,20,,Which planet are you from, Okumura?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.15,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It saw you!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.93,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.98,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go calling it!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:12.25,0:03:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seal!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.46,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{koneko}Bow to the floor to the Holy Unmovable, the Raging Destroyer King...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is one less thing to worry about.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okumura!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't move.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! I'll deal with this and catch up with you!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing this again?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.93,0:03:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Of course we'll help you!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima, your staff!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you break it!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to run!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great and mighty Unmovable Wise, crush all hesitation.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Swipe aside all obstacles. Hear our prayer. Have mercy.{http://www.sakai.zaq.ne.jp/piicats/hudou.wma}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Return!{i think he's commanding the staff back}
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, amazing!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all I can do!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.71,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you defeat {\i1}iiit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 2,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not chasing us anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.33,0:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Suguro.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.47,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just returning the favor.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.12,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Favor?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to defeat Satan just like me,
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without being embarrassed.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.58,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm stupid so I don't really think about that kinda stuff.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:56.60,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But stop trying to solve everything by yourself!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you're not alone!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon's totally right.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.62,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't defeat Satan alone.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you, even though I can't do much.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it doesn't involve more bugs.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, we're here for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shima was totally useless this time.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.99,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair, Bon! I did what I could!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.68,0:07:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they knew that I'm the son of Satan?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.23,0:07:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray, we're all back alive!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice. You're still in one piece.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:57.91,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? You're here already?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:02.12,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I made my familiars do it. Takara was even quicker though.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.27,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You took so long with so many people? Lame losers.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is he made of?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.56,0:08:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're all here? No one gave up?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who shot up the fireworks earlier?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Him? From back then?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there with your jaws on the floor!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.81,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shura!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Behemoth!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for ya.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.05,0:09:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd have a nice cup of tea while I watch the show,
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is even better than I expected.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.47,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't be so easy, Amaimon.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna kill her.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That you won't.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to kill any of them, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I apologize. I'll control myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A total barrier?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.96,0:09:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It protects everyone inside the circle and attacks everything outside.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being we're safe inside it.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But who was that guy?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:45.25,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, is this training as well?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't this a bit too tough for that!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The training's over.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're gonna prepare for Amaimon's attacks.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.52,0:09:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaimon?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.27,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaimon... One of the Eight Princes of Hell, the Earth King?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.17,0:10:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a big fish, so big you Esquires won't be able to land even a scratch on him.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:09.67,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll soak you in triple-C holy water for extra protection. Come here.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,such a big fish...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.00,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a joke?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.86,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie, that was close. It wouldn't be a pretty sight if I soaked you.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.37,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning God created the heaven and the earth.{genesis 1:1}
Dialogue: 2,0:10:36.12,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this will protect you somewhat until you dry.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not doing it to Okumura?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:45.50,0:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... He's, lessee... allergic to holy water.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.63,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Allergic to holy water?{\i0} Is that even possible?!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Yukio?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.26,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in the way so I sent him away.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.41,0:11:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon bugs of this forest are supposed to be bound to Tamers.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.97,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there an emergency number if no one picks up?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't contact the other teachers either.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.88,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's a big one like Amaimon attacking us?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.17,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.22,0:11:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno know why, but he's probably after me.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.04,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, this barrier should hold against even Amaimon.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.42,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like he's got some kinda plan this time.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.07,0:12:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time he attacks you'll leave here with the Demon-Slaying Blade.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Demon-Slaying Blade?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I bow down to beg your permission.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going on about how you wanted it back?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And weren't you supposed to suppress my power?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.16,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me not to use my flames!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already. I warned you,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but you went and used them anyway, didn't you?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.96,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it, nyahahaha~
Dialogue: 2,0:12:32.72,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is, how are you gonna fight without your flames?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.86,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Amaimon is the King of Earth, he ain't a little imp like the ones you've fought so far.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Moriyama, where are you going?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey! Someone stop her!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a parasite?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiemi!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to her?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.31,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just made a demon bug lay her egg in her.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.38,0:13:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a while for it to hatch and connect to the nerves though.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But now she'll do whatever I command.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you broccoli!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! I'll follow you!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.38,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okumura!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:47.68,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're staying in there no matter what happens! Got it?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.21,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing it again...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you want from me?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need Shiemi for?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.22,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll make her my wife!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.92,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.39,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you promise to be faithful to me in good times and in bad,
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in sickness and in health?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.70,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you love me and honor me
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all the days of your life?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.84,0:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then seal this covenant with a kiss.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold back a little, dammit.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you draw your sword?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so pretentious.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.67,0:15:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That shithead!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon, don't!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, she told us to stay here!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.54,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bon, calm down...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.68,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it's been a while since the last time I was pissed off this badly.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wipe your ass with that "calm down"!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this again...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.61,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me! Stop! You'll get yourselves killed!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.92,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I surrounded by nothing but idiots? I can't go along!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{CM}
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellooo?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.26,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this girl important to you?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you taking this seriously?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop dead!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I don't need her anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.72,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I could take one of her eyes as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.06,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our cousins has this hobby of collecting human eyeballs, he asked me to bring him some.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.66,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you leaving us out of the fun? We're joing in!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:13.94,0:18:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okumura! Get out of there if you have a chance!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:17.87,0:18:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to save Moriyama.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, go back!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.12,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Koneko, what are you trying to do to Moriyama?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.06,0:18:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Neko?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Konekomaru!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you laughing at me?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no business with you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:14.96,0:19:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okumura's the one who's pissing me off!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.69,0:19:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You act all random, then you save a person...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.19,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no talent, then you save the day...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure you out!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.91,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to be ignored.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.37,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't defeat Satan alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll help you, even though I can't do much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rin, we're here for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't forget that you're not alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.42,0:20:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys... you were all so kind to me...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:09.87,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:11.04,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap! Don't listen to him!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukio, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.71,0:20:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at lying and tricking people.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:25.82,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my power for a gentler purpose!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:50.96,0:20:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! I'll play with you!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:02.89,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening to Okumura?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.71,0:21:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a demon sword... the Kurikara.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn to ashes!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:29.49,0:21:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tail is one of the weakest points a demon has.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:32.23,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An educated demon {gentle-de-man }would know better and keep it hidden.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.29,0:21:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have loads to learn.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:39.41,0:21:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,First, your own desires.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.71,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:49.69,0:21:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:51.10,0:21:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I dealt with Amaimon's pet. I wasn't slacking off!
Dialogue: 2,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here, it's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.79,0:22:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted me to take care of this beast, Shiro?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:07.24,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:15.35,0:22:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to demons who always seek the pleasure in denial,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.81,0:22:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the moderate ways of humans are easy to corrupt.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.75,0:22:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which way are you taking?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.71,0:22:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.49,0:22:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This power... It's just like Father's!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.87,0:23:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful. I didn't think he could overwhelm Amaimon like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.34,0:23:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought enough. Enjoy your rest.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.46,0:23:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eins! Zwei! Drei!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.63,0:23:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{Kuchens Kuckucksuhr!}Cuckoo Clock!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:33.79,0:23:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:49.31,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's totally lost control of his flames.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:56.84,0:23:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:00.16,0:24:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What a handful you are, my little brother.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 2,0:25:40.86,0:25:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blue, no matter how I look at it.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:43.25,0:25:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that night.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:46.19,0:25:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That demon there is the son of Satan?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:49.54,0:25:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:51.23,0:25:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll execute the offspring of Satan!
