Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.50,OP,,0,0,0,,Fuck this destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.13,OP,,0,0,0,,I cry for my pride, I can't bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:30.63,OP,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah, ah, alone in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}An aria of love resounding through
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.30,OP,,0,0,0,,this distorted reality of twisted prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.14,OP,,0,0,0,,My dreams and tomorrow are collapsing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:41.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,230)}because throwing away the lies would be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,430)}Good bye precious life.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Go and repaint this destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.36,OP,,0,0,0,,try it for your pride, covered in wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.86,OP,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah, ah, alone in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.49,OP,,0,0,0,,Even so, I sing the song of love and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:55.70,OP,,0,0,0,,let its wish reach through this distorted world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.54,OP,,0,0,0,,to build our bonds and the tomorrow to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}Throwing away the lies was important after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:05.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,430)}because this is my precious life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:08.63,OP,,0,0,0,,Dark cloud in my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:11.59,OP,,0,0,0,,disappearing and light is shining on the road I'm on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.47,OP,,0,0,0,,Let's fight, there's no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,820)}I brandished my two-edged sword.
