Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.19,0:24:17.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(140,980)}(WIRED...)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.94,0:24:21.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(270,0)}I'm lightly fluttering in wondrous light
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:25.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,440)}like a dancing butterfly in midair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.41,0:24:29.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(270,500)}Is this place in another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:34.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(140,820)}My fall isn't slowing down so
Dialogue: 1,0:24:33.87,0:24:37.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(220,480)}cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.50,0:24:40.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(250,0)}Cut the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.34,0:24:42.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The numbers that make my head spin
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.09,0:24:43.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(0,230)}are forming a rising spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.97,0:24:47.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}and there I notice a terrible error.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.43,0:24:51.22,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Connecting people to one another
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.22,0:24:54.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}is a shining pale indigo blue wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.73,0:24:58.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's beautiful like a thread of silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.69,0:25:02.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wonder if it's what they call the chains of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.86,0:25:06.15,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.15,0:25:08.07,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.07,0:25:10.28,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}What is wired life?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.28,0:25:13.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.75,0:25:16.04,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.04,0:25:17.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}wired life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.83,0:25:21.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.21,0:25:23.13,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
