Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.34,0:25:28.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}You're a beautiful fool in
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.76,0:25:31.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1}the way you get entwined in it.
